Don't worry about what other people think... they don't matter <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   If <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> you</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> feel you earned your Orb, you did.<br>
<br>
But if you're fishing for opinions, I don't see a problem with it.  Multi-questing is questionable in certain cases, but you are of a high enough level to kill or help kill those things, and you sound like you at least tried before multi-questing(with the exception of PoA), so I don't see why it would be bad.  I'm guessing that had you not had plans that Saturday, you would have gotten the crown on the raid, right?<br>
<br>
