<br>
I mean seriously some people think that this game is more important than having a functional life.  At this point I have completed every piece of my EPIC myself.  I am down to the Burning Embers, Torch, Cloak, Earth Staff, and Crown.  The first three I will complete given time but the second two basically might just be past me because I honestly can say that the game means less than my life.<br>
